column5:
The place I go to for massage, I see the same girl. She asked me once when massaging my jawline if I had issues with the jaw, it's not in my file.

We both kinda laughed when I explained, "you ever see the thing that goes around as a reminder to relax your jaw and shoulders?" and she knew exactly what I was talking about.

Always a good reminder, thank you.
You could try Miss Carly's. [Her facebook page.](https://m.facebook.com/misscarlys/)
